<!-- Main jumbotron for a primary marketing message or call to action -->
<div class="jumbotron">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="display-3">Hello, h00man!</h1>

    <p>My coworker needed a way to add our corporate logo to images easily, so naturally instead of writing a simple
      script or using an Automator workflow, I dediced to code an entire web application!</p>

